<? read_starfish_conf(); $t= "Text::Ngrams version $ModuleVersion";
echo "$t\n".'='x length($t); !>
#+
Text::Ngrams version 2.007
==========================
#-


This is a module for flexible N-gram analysis of a text.  It supports
character n-grams, word n-grams, and more.  Documentation is a part of
the file Ngrams.pm in the pod format.  To convert it into manual page
format, type something like the following:

	  pod2html Ngrams.pm

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

No significant dependecies, as far as I know.  Let me know if you find
something important to add.

